data.description: Welcome to a your dream home, where practicality awaits in this stunning home set on just under an acre of horse property. This meticulously crafted residence offers an idyllic lifestyle with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a well-thought-out floor plan. This home offers an upgraded kitchen, boasting beautiful cabinets and granite countertops, creating a space where cooking becomes a delight. Step outside into the upgraded patio, an extension of the living space designed for entertainment and relaxation. With overhead fans creating a gentle breeze, the patio is a year-round retreat. The built-in BBQ adds a touch of luxury, creating an outdoor culinary experience that perfectly complements the indoor kitchen. Imagine evenings spent under the stars, enjoying the company of friends and family in this enchanting outdoor haven. For those seeking additional flexibility or rental income, the property features an Accessory Dwelling Unit (ADU). This separate living space provides a myriad of possibilities, whether for guests, extended family, or as a source of rental income. The ADU is a great addition to the property. the property offers ample room for RV and trailer parking. As you explore the property, you'll discover that every detail has been considered to enhance the overall experience. In conclusion, this beautiful home on horse property with an ADU is a rare find. It is more than a residence; it is a sanctuary. Don't miss the opportunity to make this enchanting property your own – a place where every day feels like a retreat, and where the memories created will be cherished for a lifetime
